data.description: This truly STUNNING Home is Nestled in the Prestigious Gated Community of HIDEAWAY BEACH and is Within Walking Distance to Private Beach, Restaurant, Bar and Grill, Tennis, GOLF and Beach Front Community Pool. ASSUMABLE 2.375% VA Loan (do not need to be a veteran) Built by DIVCO this CUSTOM Built Home is BRIGHT, OPEN AND AIRY. Open Kitchen Concept with Large BREAKFAST BAR, ALL New UPGRADED Appliances and Separate Dining Area that Flows into the Large Great Room. Complete with High Ceilings, Crown Molding, and 10' Impact Pocketed Sliding Doors that Bring the ELEGANT OUTDOOR LIVING SPACE in. Private Master Bedroom features Large Master Bath, SOAKING TUB, Large Walk In Shower and Dual Sinks. This SPECTACULAR Home Offers 3 Bedrooms (1 EN SUITE), 3 ½ Baths and Separate OFFICE / DEN, New ELEVATOR (2021), WHOLE HOUSE OWNED SOLAR PANELS and Whole House BATTERY BACK UP and New Cat5 High Speed Network. Step Out to the Private OUTDOOR LIVING SPACE with Saltwater Pool and CASCADING WATERFALL SPA. LARGE 3 CAR GARAGE and Over $160,000 of recent upgrades Include: New Elevator (2021), New Whole House Solar (2021), LG Oversized Washer and Dryer, New Furnishings (2021) Negotiable, New 30 KW Backup Battery and New A/C (2021). HIDEAWAY BEACH LIFESTYLE includes PRIVATE BEACH, Beachfront Swimming pool and Spa, Sports Center, Executive Golf Course, Fine Dining, Poolside Bar/Grill, Tennis, Pickleball, Kayaking and 24 hour gated community. THIS IS ISLAND LIVING AT ITS FINEST AND IS TRULY A MUST SEE!!!!
